The Keiser Report  No. 96
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 18 November 2010


[sebaygo1]


Markets! Finance! Silver! 

Max and Stacy look at the call from Eric Cantona to withdraw money from the banks, and at the viral Crash JP Morgan Buy Silver campaign by Max Keiser. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Alex Jones about Google bombs, naked body scanners and Crash JP Morgan Buy Silver.



The .mp3 is audio extracted from the Russia Today video.
